Liao Ting Yan.

28
00:03:53,110 --> 00:03:57,340
 Why did she enter my dream without permission
and stir my heart? 

29
00:03:58,150 --> 00:04:00,520
 Why did she show up here 

30
00:04:01,420 --> 00:04:03,650
 by coincidence? 

31
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,730
 There's something more to this
than meets the eye. 

32
00:04:09,730 --> 00:04:13,840
 I cannot just let my guard down
because of that dream. 

33
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:20,880
Why did you cry?

34
00:04:21,830 --> 00:04:24,870
In the realm of mortals,
absence stirs no grief.

35
00:04:26,610 --> 00:04:29,050
But when we meet again, grief blossoms at once.

36
00:04:29,050 --> 00:04:30,980
Do you know me?

37
00:04:32,890 --> 00:04:35,470
Of course I know you.

38
00:04:35,470 --> 00:04:37,520
Have we met before?

39
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:40,130
This is our first encounter in this lifetime.

40
00:04:40,130 --> 00:04:41,880
In this lifetime?

41
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:47,580
 ♫ Mountains and rivers shatter before my eyes ♫ 

42
