43
00:04:50,780 --> 00:04:53,740
If so, why did you come to me?

44
00:04:54,490 --> 00:04:56,640
Just to see you.

45
00:04:58,590 --> 00:05:00,390
You look the same.

46
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:04,730
However, those clear eyes, the gentle contours,

47
00:05:04,730 --> 00:05:07,790
and that tender face brimming with freshness...

48
00:05:10,370 --> 00:05:13,860
Are you the legendary 19-year-old boy?

49
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:19,620
 ♫ Like heavy rain pouring down ♫ 

50
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:23,600
 ♫ Drunk on romance. In a blink ♫ 

51
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:28,400
 ♫ Love and hate vanish into illusion ♫ 

52
00:05:29,020 --> 00:05:31,370
What nonsense are you talking about?

53
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:35,540
Do you know who I am?

54
00:05:39,730 --> 00:05:41,760
You are Sima Jiao.

55
00:05:42,290 --> 00:05:44,900
You're the emperor of Hu Kingdom.

56
00:05:47,170 --> 00:05:52,190
If so, have you heard that I've slain countless lives?

57
00:05:56,540 --> 00:06:01,050
I once peeled the skin of an individual
who criticized me harshly

58
00:06:01,050 --> 00:06:03,100
and hung it on the palace wall

59
00:06:03,100 --> 00:06:05,710
until the wind and rain wore him down,

60
00:06:05,710 --> 00:06:08,550
leaving nothing but a white skeleton.

61
00:06:08,550 --> 00:06:11,320
 In the past, you would vanquish
one's clan for no reason. 

62
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:15,030
 You would blow up half of
Gengchen Celestial Palace with a spell. 

63
00:06:15,030 --> 00:06:19,040
 You would reduce demon generals to ashes just so you could use them as fertilizer. 

64
00:06:21,980 --> 00:06:24,980
I'm not one to appreciate delicate beauty.

65
00:06:28,170 --> 00:06:32,460
- What are you smiling at?
- I'm smiling at how adorable you've become.

66
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:38,320
 ♫ Stirring waves, upending a lifetime ♫ 

67
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:41,540
